## Report Specifications
- **Format:** IEEE style, minimum 10 pages[cite: 2].
- **Sections Required:**
  1. Executive Summary [cite: 2]
  2. Introduction [cite: 2]
  3. Data Analysis and Data Preprocess (Stats, viz, preprocessing logic) [cite: 2]
  4. Methods (Model rationale, hyperparameters, tuning, comparisons) [cite: 2]
  5. Results (Test set metrics, visual outputs) [cite: 2]
  6. Discussion (Findings, future work) [cite: 2]
